      • ApproximateProgressMeasure

        public ApproximateProgressMeasure(Game game,
                                  StateSet subgame,
                                  GamePlayer player,
                                  int ds)
        Initializes this progress measure for a subgame of a parity game. All tuples are (0, 0, ..., 0) after initialization.
        Parameters:
        game - a parity game
        subgame - the states of the subgame
        player - the game player which the solver is going to solve the parity game for
        ds - the maximum sum of all tuples in this progress measure
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the game is not a parity game
